<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA512_04_SU_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_04.css" />

    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema512_04_0006.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_04_su_0006" data-current-page="page_3, page_5">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="4_green" lang="y">여러 수의 곱으로 나타낸 식을 이용하여 12와 18의 최대공약수를 구하는 방법을 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <div class="input_area">
                <article class="page page_1">
                    <h3 lang="y">12와 18을 각각 두 수의 곱으로 나타내고, 공약수와 최대공약수를 구해 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="page_1_cont">
                        <div class="question_box flex justify_evenly">
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>12=1&times;12</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>12=2&times;6</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>12=</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <span>&times;4</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="question_box flex justify_evenly">
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>18=1&times;18</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>18=2&times;9</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>18=3&times;</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="example_comment flex justify_evenly">
                            <p lang="y">12와 18의 공약수</p>
                            <p lang="y">12와 18의 최대공약수</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="question_box flex example_etc gap_12">
                            <div class="flex align_end">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                ,
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_end">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                ,
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_end">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                ,
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_end">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- 최대공약수 답부분 -->
                            <div class="flex">
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="example_img flex align_center justify_center">
                        <p lang="y">12=<span class="point_txt">2</span>&times;6, 18=<span
                                class="point_txt">2</span>&times;9 이니까 <span class="point_txt">2</span>는 12와 18의 공약수예요.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <h3 lang="y">12와 18을 각각 여러 수의 곱으로 나타내어 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="page_2_cont flex justify_center">
                        <!--page_1_cont class지우면 page2내용 틀어짐-->
                        <div class="question_box flex justify_evenly">
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>12=2&times;2&times;</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex align_center">
                                <span>18=2&times;3&times;</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap answer1 flex">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_3">
                    <h3 lang="y">여러 수의 곱에서 최대공약수를 나타내는 곱을 찾아 O표 하세요.</h3>
                    <div class="flex justify_evenly">
                        <div class="boolean_wrap align_center">
                            12=
                            <button data-answer-single="false">2&times;2</button>
                            <button data-answer-single="true">2&times;3</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="boolean_wrap align_center">
                            18=
                            <button data-answer-single="true">2&times;3</button>
                            <button data-answer-single="false">3&times;3</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_4">
                    <h3 lang="y">12와 18의 최대공약수를 곱으로 나타내어 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="question_box flex justify_evenly">
                        <div class="flex align_center">
                            <span>6=</span>
                            <div class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="2 또는 3" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["2", "3"]}'
                                    text-align="center" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                            </div>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <div class="input_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="2 또는 3" data-answer-multi='{"values": ["2", "3"]}'
                                    text-align="center" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_5">
                    <h3 lang="y">여러 수의 곱으로 나타낸 식을 이용하여 12와 18의 최대공약수를 구하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
                    <div class="page_5_cont margin_center">
                        <div class="example_img margin_center">
                            <div class="flex">
                                <div>
                                    <p>12=2&times;6</p>
                                    <p>12=2&times;2&times;3</p>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p>18=2&times;9</p>
                                    <p>18=2&times;3&times;3</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="summarize_wrap">
                                <div class="summarize">
                                    <div>
                                        <span lang="y">12와 18의 최대공약수:</span>
                                        <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="2x3=6" lang="y"
                                            onclick="countClick();">
                                            <span class="answerWrap">
                                                <span
                                                class="colorGreen bgGreen">2</span>&times;<span
                                                class="colorGreen">3</span>=6
                                            </span>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="etc_img">
                                <p class="example_comment" lang="y">최대공약수는 식에 공통으로 들어 있는 수를 모두 곱하면 돼.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input_wrap">
                            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                            <div class="example_box">
                                <p lang="y">여러 수의 곱으로 나타낸 식에서 공통으로 들어 있는 수를 모두 곱하면 최대공약수입니다.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset" lang="y">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnCheck" lang="y">확인</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true" onclick="addInfoImgOnlySubmit();">확인</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>